columnConfigurations.columnName: Orders created with immediate start date (%)
columnConfigurations.columnAlias: Orders created with immediate start date (%)

dataSource.query:
SELECT
	 event_name AS Variant,
    "Number of Cases",
    "Time until confirmation & technical completion (days)",
    "Time until confirmation & closing (days)",
    "Orders created with immediate start date (%)",
    "Order released late (%)",
    "Order completed late (%)"
FROM (
	SELECT
    	count(case_id) AS "Number of Cases",
        event_name AS Variant,
        AVG ("4 - Lead time from start - Maintenance orders confirmed and technically completed") 
        	AS "Time until confirmation & technical completion (days)",
		AVG ("4 - Lead time from start - Maintenance orders confirmed and closed") 
        	AS "Time until confirmation & closing (days)",
		AVG ("2 - Blocker - Maintenance orders created with immediate basic start date") * 100 
        	AS "Orders created with immediate start date (%)",
		AVG ("2 - Blocker - Maintenance orders released after basic start date") * 100 
        	AS "Order released late (%)",
		AVG ("2 - Blocker - Maintenance orders technically completed after basic finish date") * 100 
        	AS "Order completed late (%)"
	FROM THIS_PROCESS
    GROUP BY 2
) AS sub
ORDER BY 2 DESC
LIMIT 5
